Game.....: Sports Jam
Origin...: USA - NTSC
Released.: July 19th, 2001
Ripped.......: Nothing

From the same group that brought you the Japanese version of this  game comes the English translation. Have fun.

Straight from the arcade hit to your Sega Dreamcast - Sports Jam  is loaded with eight competitive sports for you to master in head-to-head 2-player matches. The goal is to earn the title of King of Sports, and this can only be done by mastering all 12 events! Football, Baseball, Hockey, Basketball, Tennis, Soccer, Golf and Cycling - each of these sports features fully rendered 3D characters and background graphics that enhance some of the toughest sports challenges ever simulated!